originalText.text: I have had facial surgery with Dr. Keegan twice over the years and have been so happy with the results.   The reason I went to him was he did a friends surgery and she looked wonderful, not pulled, stretched just very natural.  He will tell u if you want to do too much.  I think he is wonderful surgeon,  and also a very nice person.

originalText.text: I cannot say enough great things about Dr. Keegan.  Dr. Keegan is very thorough with great attention to detail.  He has a way of making you feel very comfortable and takes the time to explain or answer any questions you may have.  In addition, making an appointment with his office was a very pleasant experience.  The nurses and staff follow suit to Dr. Keegan's example and overall the entire experience in the office was wonderful.  I made the right choice in doctors and will definitely go back to Dr. Keegan and recommend him to others.

originalText.text:
Ruined my life.
No number of good reviews can give me back my life and what I had before me.
Primitive pimp butcher, sad incompetent- you can't even get mad at incompetence; you just wish an equal loss back to them (and there is no such thing; I was singular. you wish an equal, and equally unending, pain back.), not out of depravity, but because knowing matters: so that they may know the immensity of what they took.
